              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "- By Authors - The binary and ternary fission induced",
                "by high-energy particles is defined as a decay of the",
                "nucleus into two resp. three fragments of approximately",
                "equal masses."
              ]
            }
